<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>在<code v-pre>application.yml</code>中进行配置</strong></p>
<div class="language-yaml line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="yml" data-title="yml"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token key atrule">spring</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token key atrule">redis</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span></span>
